high_descs: Turn around and go forward to the chair, then hang a left and go to the table with the TV on it.
Pick up the white plate that is on the bottom shelf of the table with the TV on it.
Turn around and go to the right side of the table in front of the couch.
Put the white plate on top of the table.
Turn around and go forward, then hang a left and go to the dining table that will be on the left.
Pick up the white plate that is at the end of the dining table.
Turn around and go to the wall, go to the right past the couch, hang a right and go to the table that is in front of the couch.
Put the white plate on the table behind the other white plate.
anns.task_desc: Put two plates on a table.

high_descs: Move to the TV stand to the right of you
Pick up plate from the stand
Move to the coffee table behind you
Place plate on the table
Move to the dining to the right of the couch to the right
Pick up plate from the table
Move to the coffee table to the left of you
Place plate on the table
anns.task_desc: Put two plates on the coffee table.

high_descs: Turn to your right, then go around the right of the coffee table to the TV stand.
Pick up the plate from the shelf below the TV stand.
Turn around to your left and go to the end of the coffee table that is on your left.
Put the plate between the other objects on the coffee table.
Turn right and go between the right side of the sofa and the wall, then turn left to face the end of the dining table.
Pick up the plate from the near left corner of the table.
Retrace your path to the coffee table.
Put the plate onto the coffee table, beyond the other plate.
anns.task_desc: Move two plates to a coffee table.
